      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。Idle是初始状态对吧？那PaymentGateway本身要作为一个整体入口吗，还是只作为状态机的名称？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "Idle"
