    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Idle是初始状态。PaymentGateway作为整个状态机的上下文入口，用那种方括号的形式标注在顶部。然后Idle通过Start事件触发到Active。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "Idle",
        "Active",
        "Start"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把基础结构搭出来：PaymentGateway指向Idle，Idle通过Start迁移到Active。接下来Active要能回到Idle吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "Idle",
        "Active",
        "Start"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，用Stop事件回到Idle。另外关键的一点是Active状态要连接到AuthVault，表示鉴权验证的环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "Idle",
        "Stop",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Stop是从Active回到Idle，然后Active到AuthVault是一条直接的连线，不需要标注事件名称？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "Idle",
        "Stop",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Active到AuthVault保持简洁就好，不用额外标注。整体就是个简单的Idle-Active循环，加上鉴权节点的状态机。",
      "elements_involved": [
